<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{#if isUpgrade}}Plan Upgraded{{else}}Plan Changed{{/if}} - Roastr.ai</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            {{#if isUpgrade}}
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            {{else}}
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            {{/if}}
            color: white;
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
            margin: -20px -20px 30px -20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .header .emoji {
            font-size: 48px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .plan-comparison {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid {{#if isUpgrade}}#10b981{{else}}#f59e0b{{/if}};
        }
        .plan-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .plan-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .plan-old {
            color: #6b7280;
            text-decoration: line-through;
        }
        .plan-new {
            color: {{#if isUpgrade}}#10b981{{else}}#f59e0b{{/if}};
        }
        .arrow {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        .features-list {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features-list h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #111827;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .features-list ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .features-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 30px;
        }
        .features-list li:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            color: #10b981;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 8px;
        }
        .features-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: {{#if isUpgrade}}#10b981{{else}}#3b82f6{{/if}};
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: {{#if isUpgrade}}#059669{{else}}#2563eb{{/if}};
        }
        .effective-date {
            background: #fef3c7;
            color: #92400e;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            .header {
                margin: -20px -20px 20px -20px;
            }
            .plan-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .arrow {
                transform: rotate(90deg);
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <span class="emoji">{{#if isUpgrade}}ðŸš€{{else}}ðŸ”„{{/if}}</span>
            <h1>{{#if isUpgrade}}Plan Upgraded Successfully!{{else}}Plan Changed{{/if}}</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

            {{#if isUpgrade}}
                <p>Great news! Your plan has been successfully upgraded and all new features are now active and ready to use.</p>
            {{else}}
                <p>Your subscription plan has been updated as requested.</p>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="plan-comparison">
                <div class="plan-row">
                    <span class="plan-name plan-old">{{oldPlanName}}</span>
                    <span class="arrow">â†’</span>
                    <span class="plan-name plan-new">{{newPlanName}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="effective-date">
                <strong>Effective Date:</strong> {{effectiveDate}}
            </div>

            {{#if newFeatures}}
                {{#if newFeatures.length}}
                    <div class="features-list">
                        <h3>{{#if isUpgrade}}Your New Features{{else}}Current Plan Features{{/if}}</h3>
                        <ul>
                            {{#each newFeatures}}
                                <li>{{this}}</li>
                            {{/each}}
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                {{/if}}
            {{/if}}

            {{#if isUpgrade}}
                <p>ðŸŽ‰ <strong>You're all set!</strong> Start exploring your new features right away. If you have any questions about your upgrade, we're here to help.</p>
            {{else}}
                <p>Your plan change is now active. If you have any questions about your new plan or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out.</p>
            {{/if}}

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">Go to Dashboard</a>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Need help?</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #6b7280;">
                <li>Visit your <a href="{{billingUrl}}">billing settings</a> to manage your subscription</li>
                <li>Check out our help center for guides and tutorials</li>
                <li>Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent by Roastr.ai</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p><a href="{{billingUrl}}">Manage Subscription</a> | <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}">Dashboard</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>